  "commentary": "With SPX at 7030.58 sitting right between the max negative gamma at 7015 and the massive positive gamma wall at 7050, dealers are likely modestly buying the dip here as we're above the flip at 6872 in PIN regime. The recent wall_break event combined with strong positive momentum (4.7% 5-min change) suggests we're testing into the heavy 7030-7050 gamma wall cluster where dealers will increasingly sell rallies to hedge their long gamma positions. Key levels to watch are the 7015 negative gamma strike below (dealer buying support) and the 7050 max positive gamma wall above (heavy dealer selling pressure).\n\nBottom line: expect price to get sticky and face resistance as we approach 7050 with potential pullback toward 7015.",
